- 4 commits made; push skipped (no remote configured)

**Key design choices:**
- Token recording is async (`go recordTokens(...)`) so SSE streams aren't delayed by disk I/O
- `http.Client{Timeout: 0}` — no timeout for long-running streaming requests
- `stats` is a subcommand of the same binary (no separate `ctx-proxy` binary needed for Phase 1)
- Session survives proxy restarts within the gap window by loading `session.json` on startup
